Yes.

16:25.200 --> 16:26.451
After Peter showed up

16:26.500 --> 16:28.627
and interrupted Mr. Locke

16:28.680 --> 16:30.102
and asked ifI had
Mirandized him.

16:30.160 --> 16:31.502
