are offering

22:42.830 --> 22:44.309
Mr. McVeigh's testimony

22:44.360 --> 22:46.009
to show Governor Florrick's
state of mind.

22:46.060 --> 22:47.448
_His state of mind
is irrelevant here.

22:47.490 --> 22:49.799
It-it's his action...

22:49.840 --> 22:52.365
Governor Florrick had no reason
to lose these bullets

22:52.410 --> 22:53.798
