22:56.850 --> 22:58.238
[shushes]

22:59.900 --> 23:01.197
I'll allow.

23:01.240 --> 23:02.320
He likes her.

23:02.380 --> 23:03.893
LUCCA:
Mr. McVeigh?

23:03.940 --> 23:06.113
As a respected
ballistics expert,

23:06.160 --> 23:09.118
who has worked for
the SA's office for ten years--

23:09.170 --> 23:11.513
what was your determination
about these bullets?

23:11.560 --> 23:14.336
Well, I should say that
my findings were preliminary.

23:17.700 --> 23:19.918
But from what I saw,

23:19.960 --> 23:24.135
these bullets did not come
from Mr. Locke's gun.

23:24.180 --> 23:26.740
[laughs]
Pardon our dust.

23:26.790 --> 23:28.269
Pardon our noise.

23:28.310 --> 23:29.925
Yeah, the world has changed.

23:29.970 --> 23:31.221
People don't look

23:31.270 --> 23:33.147
