23:41.850 --> 23:44.762
Uh, the Coleman divorce,
the bitch is on the line.

23:44.810 --> 23:47.722
She wants to talk
to both of us.

23:47.770 --> 23:49.590
David, what is your problem?

23:49.640 --> 23:50.720
My problem?

23:50.770 --> 23:52.499
Yes, there is
no Coleman divorce.

23:52.560 --> 23:54.425
My problem is I'm
an equity partner.

23:54.470 --> 23:55.778
