24:08.180 --> 24:09.522
it's discriminatory.

24:09.570 --> 24:10.832
Oh, come on,
you know what we were doing.

24:10.880 --> 24:12.131
You've been on
a hiring binge,

24:12.180 --> 24:13.226
and how many men
have you interviewed?

24:13.270 --> 24:15.056
How many male lavwers

24:15.100 --> 24:16.488
have you met with?

24:16.540 --> 24:18.963
I have met with men.Watch it, Diane.

24:19.020 --> 24:21.056
