in your future.

24:21.110 --> 24:22.054
[door opens]

24:22.110 --> 24:24.886
[Jason clears throat]

24:24.940 --> 24:27.329
This is an affidavit
from a coworker

24:27.370 --> 24:28.325
of Geneva Pine.

24:28.370 --> 24:30.156
He says that Geneva often

24:30.200 --> 24:34.079
bullied her way
into other cases.

24:35.730 --> 24:37.504
That's it? Nothing else?

24:37.560 --> 24:38.720
