24:38.780 --> 24:40.429
Just time and dates

24:40.470 --> 24:42.995
and she had some issues
with back taxes.

24:43.040 --> 24:45.088
Nothing about her
sleeping with Peter?

24:48.790 --> 24:51.429
Nothing I could
confirm independently.

24:51.490 --> 24:54.789
Did you try
to confirm it independently?

24:58.100 --> 24:59.749
I'm just...

24:59.800 --> 25:01.836
I'm in a awkward position here.

25:01.890 --> 25:04.620
I know.

25:04.670 --> 25:07.366
