Take it to him.

39:25.140 --> 39:27.745
And sell it.

39:27.800 --> 39:29.927
Before the jury comes back.

39:33.020 --> 39:34.009
We're not giving up.

39:34.060 --> 39:35.186
We're working
different angles.

39:35.240 --> 39:36.662
Mike T_as_cioni found
a criminal case

39:36.720 --> 39:38.324
against an SA.
in DuPage County

39:38.370 --> 39:40.804
in '98 that was
thrown out.

39:40.850 --> 39:42.408
He thinks we can mine it
for a precedent.

39:42.460 --> 39:43.540
Eli, can you give us a minute?

39:47.120 --> 39:48.508
Yes, of course.

39:48.560 --> 39:49.766
I'm so sorry.

39:49.820 --> 39:51.071
[footfalls receding]

39:53.600 --> 39:54.942
[glasses clink]

39:59.300 --> 40:00.517
[cork pops]

40:07.310 --> 40:10.222
Can I make a confession to you?

40:10.270 --> 40:13.398
Sure.

40:13.450 --> 40:16.089
I never liked wine.

40:17.500 --> 40:19.456
I only drank it
'cause you liked it.

40:19.500 --> 40:20.888
I was always
a Scotch guy.

40:20.940 --> 40:22.669
I guess I inherited that
from my father.

40:22.720 --> 40:23.937
[laughs]

40:23.980 --> 40:25.675
Well, I can fix you a Scotch.

40:25.720 --> 40:26.937
No.

40:26.980 --> 40:28.504
It's grown on me.

40:35.820 --> 40:39.039
Two years.

40:40.520 --> 40:42.249
Oh, God...

40:42.300 --> 40:43.858
I was in there for
only eight months

40:43.910 --> 40:45.309
and almost died.

40:45.350 --> 40:47.136
Wait for the verdict, Peter.

40:47.180 --> 40:48.738
I do that,

40:48.790 --> 40:51.258
I may actually die in prison.

40:51.310 --> 40:52.527
Ten years.

40:56.270 --> 40:57.749
What did you think of the jury?

41:00.020 --> 41:02.238
I think they were judging us.

41:02.280 --> 41:05.238
But I think your speech
at the end went over well.

41:06.940 --> 41:08.589
I was always good with a speech.

41:11.120 --> 41:14.760
There's no good answer,
is there?

41:17.300 --> 41:19.689
I don't know
what to say.

41:24.430 --> 41:26.773
I'm not good at gambling.

41:30.480 --> 41:32.914
Don't decide yet, Peter.

41:32.960 --> 41:35.269
The jury's retired.

41:35.310 --> 41:38.609
Just... sleep on it.

41:42.060 --> 41:43.755
I'm gonna take the deal.

41:47.590 --> 41:49.546
It's the smart
thing to do.

41:51.590 --> 41:53.103
Two years.

41:55.070 --> 41:57.288
I'll get out,

41:57.340 --> 41:59.763
write a book,
start over.

42:02.430 --> 42:05.126
Are you gonna
come visit me?

42:05.170 --> 42:06.649
I will.

42:09.740 --> 42:12.527
The hardest thing
is being forgotten.

42:14.270 --> 42:19.173
I won't forget.

42:19.230 --> 42:20.527
Okay.

42:23.880 --> 42:25.188
[sighs]

42:25.230 --> 42:27.232
[phone buzzes]

42:34.070 --> 42:35.970
What?

42:36.030 --> 42:38.191
The jury's back.

